    <lb n="1"/><supplied reason="lost">βασιλεῖ Πτολεμ</supplied>αίωι καὶ βασιλίσσηι Κλεοπάτραι τῆι ἀδελφῆι καὶ βασ<supplied reason="lost">ιλ</supplied>ίσσηι 

    <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">Κλεοπάτραι</supplied> τῆ<supplied reason="lost">ι γυ</supplied>ναικὶ θεοῖς Εὐεργέταις χαίρειν 

    <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">Μεγχῆς</supplied> κωμο<supplied reason="lost">γ</supplied>ραμματεὺς Κερκεοσίρεως τῆς Πολέμωνος μερίδος τοῦ 

    <lb n="4"/>Ἀρ<supplied reason="lost">σ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined">ιν</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ο</supplied><unclear reason="undefined">ί</unclear><supplied reason="lost">του</supplied> καὶ ὁ τούτου ἀδελφὸς <choice><corr>Πο<supplied reason="omitted">λέ</supplied>μων.</corr><sic>πομων</sic></choice> τῆι <num value="17">ιζ</num> τοῦ Ἁθ<supplied reason="lost">ὺρ το</supplied>ῦ ἐνεστῶτος 

    <lb n="5"/><num value="53">νγ</num> <expan><ex>ἔτους</ex></expan> προ<unclear reason="undefined">σπε</unclear><supplied reason="lost">σό</supplied>ντος ἡμῖν Ἀσκληπιάδην τινὰ τῶν παρ᾽ Ἀμιν<supplied reason="lost">ίου</supplied> 

    <lb n="6"/>τοῦ ἐπιστάτου τῶν φυλακιτῶν τοῦ αὐτοῦ νομοῦ παραγείνεσθαι 

    <lb n="7"/>εἰς τὴν κώμ<supplied reason="lost">ην κ</supplied>αὶ κατὰ τὸ <app type="BL"><lem resp="1.423"><unclear reason="undefined">καθ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ῆκ</supplied>ον</lem><rdg><gap reason="illegible" extent="3" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" extent="2" unit="character"/>ον</rdg></app> παρεγενήθημεν εἰς ἀπάντησιν 

    <lb n="8"/>σὺν τῶι τῆς κώμης κωμάρχωι <supplied reason="lost">καί</supplied> <choice><corr>τισι</corr><sic>τινων</sic></choice> τῶν πρεσβυτέρων τῶν 

    <lb n="9"/><supplied reason="lost">γ</supplied>εωργῶν καὶ Δημητρίωι τῶι διεξάγοντι τὰ κατὰ τὴν ἐπιστατείαν 

    <lb n="10"/>καὶ ἀρχιφυλακιτείαν τῆς αὐτῆς καὶ ἄλλοις, οὐδεμίαν ἔχοντες 

    <lb n="11"/><gap reason="lost" extent="1" unit="character"/><unclear reason="undefined">αμινω</unclear>ν<unclear reason="undefined">τ</unclear><gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/><unclear reason="undefined">ω</unclear>ν ἐξεδεξιασάμεθα αὐτόν, καὶ ἐπίλημψιν ἡμῶν 

    <lb n="12"/>ἐποιήσατο ὁμ<supplied reason="lost">οίως</supplied> δὲ καὶ τοῦ Δημητρίου καὶ ἑνὸς τῶν γεωργῶν 

    <lb n="13"/><choice><corr>Μαρρείους</corr><sic>μαρρην</sic></choice> Πετ<unclear reason="undefined">ῶτ</unclear>ος, προφερόμενος ἐπιδεδόσθαι κατὰ ἡμῶν 

    <lb n="14"/>καὶ Μαρώνος τ<supplied reason="lost">οῦ</supplied> Διοδώρου καὶ Πετεσούχ<supplied reason="lost">ο</supplied>υ <supplied reason="lost">τοῦ </supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="5" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost"> ο</supplied>υ καὶ 

    <lb n="15"/>Σίμωνος τοῦ <gap reason="lost" extent="3" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost"> ο</supplied>υ τῶν ἐκ τῆ<supplied reason="lost">ς</supplied> αὐτῆς καὶ Ἀρτε<supplied reason="lost">μιδώ</supplied>ρ<supplied reason="lost">ου κω</supplied><unclear reason="undefined">μ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ο</supplied>-

    <lb n="16"/>γραμματέως <supplied reason="lost">Ἰβίωνο</supplied>ς <expan><ex>Εἰκοσιπενταρούρων</ex></expan> προσαγγελίαν ὑπὸ Ἁρυώτου τοῦ 

    <lb n="17"/>Ἁρσιγήσιος τ<supplied reason="lost">ῶν</supplied> <unclear reason="undefined">ἀ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">πὸ Κροκο</supplied><unclear reason="undefined">δ</unclear>ίλων πόλεως <del rend="erasure"><gap reason="illegible" extent="4" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/>ος</del> ὡς <del rend="erasure"><gap reason="illegible" extent="4" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/>υλη</del> 

    <lb n="18"/>συνδεδειπνη<supplied reason="lost">κό</supplied>των <choice><corr>αὐτῶι</corr><sic>αυτων</sic></choice> ἔν τινι <choice><corr>καπηλείωι</corr><sic>καπηληωι</sic></choice> ἐν τῆι κώμηι 

    <lb n="19"/>καὶ <choice><corr>ἐπανῄρηται</corr><sic>επανειρηται</sic></choice> <choice><corr>αὐτὸς</corr><sic>αυτον</sic></choice> φαρμάκωι, ὑφ᾽ <supplied reason="lost">ο</supplied>ὗ καὶ ἀναχθέντες ἐπὶ τὸν 

    <lb n="20"/>Ἀμινίαν τῇ <num value="19">ιθ</num> τοῦ αὐτοῦ μηνὸς ἐξ ἐπισκέψεως παρόντος καὶ 

    <lb n="21"/>Ἀμεννέως τοῦ <expan>βα<ex>σιλικοῦ</ex></expan> <expan>γρ<ex>αμματέως</ex></expan> παραχρῆμα ἀπελύθημεν διὰ τὸ <app type="BL"><lem resp="7.269"><choice><corr>ἀν<supplied reason="omitted">αι</supplied>τίους</corr><sic>αντιους</sic></choice></lem><rdg>ἀντίου?</rdg></app> 


    <lb n="22"/><app type="BL"><lem resp="7.269"><choice><corr>φανῆναι</corr><sic><unclear reason="undefined">φ</unclear>α<unclear reason="undefined">ν</unclear>ησαι</sic></choice></lem><rdg><supplied reason="lost">ἀ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined">φ</unclear>ανῆσαι</rdg></app>, ὅθεν <app type="BL"><lem resp="3.240">προορώμενοι</lem><rdg><unclear reason="undefined">προ</unclear><gap reason="illegible" extent="3" unit="character"/>ωμενοι</rdg></app> μή ποτε περὶ τῶν αὐτῶν 

    <lb n="23"/><gap reason="lost" extent="22" unit="character"/><unclear reason="undefined">τ</unclear>ου <subst><add place="inline">ἀναστρεφομέν<unclear reason="undefined">ω</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ν</supplied></add><del rend="corrected">αποστρεφομεν<unclear reason="undefined">ω</unclear></del></subst> <supplied reason="lost">π</supplied>αρε-

    <lb n="24"/><supplied reason="lost">νοχληθῶμεν μηδὲ </supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="4" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" extent="2" unit="character"/>τι<unclear reason="undefined">μωι</unclear> τῶν <choice><corr>προσαγγελέν<supplied reason="lost">τω</supplied>ν</corr><sic><subst><add place="inline">προσαγγελλεν<supplied reason="lost">τω</supplied>ν</add><del rend="corrected">προσαγγελαν<supplied reason="lost">τω</supplied>ν</del></subst></sic></choice> 
</ab></div><div type="textpart" n="2"><!--milestone unit="4"--><ab>

    <lb n="25"/>ὑφ᾽ ἡμῶν ἔν τισιν ἠγνοηκότων ἐν τοῖς ὑμῖν 

    <lb n="26"/>ἀνήκουσι συκοφαντηθῶμεν <choice><corr>διασε<supplied reason="omitted">σε</supplied>ισμένων</corr><sic>διασεισμεν<unclear reason="undefined">ω</unclear>ν</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="27"/>προήγμεθα τὴν ἐφ᾽ ὑμᾶς <choice><corr>καταφυγὴν</corr><sic>καταφ<gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/><unclear reason="undefined">υ</unclear>γην</sic></choice> ποιήσασθαι, 

    <lb n="28"/>δεόμεθα, θεοὶ μέγιστοι νικηφόροι, <subst><add place="inline">μερίσαντας</add><del rend="corrected">μερισαντ<gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/></del></subst> καὶ 

    <lb n="29"/>ἡμῖν ἧς ἔχετε πρὸς πάντας ἀντιλήμψεως, 

    <lb n="30"/><subst><add place="inline">ἐπεὶ</add><del rend="corrected">επιι</del></subst> ἐξ ἐπισκέψεως ἐν <subst><add place="inline">συνεδρίαι</add><del rend="corrected">συνεδρ<del rend="erasure">ω</del>ιαι</del></subst> <subst><add place="inline">παρόντος</add><del rend="corrected">παρ<gap reason="illegible" extent="4" unit="character"/></del></subst> 

    <lb n="31"/>καὶ <del rend="erasure">παρόντος</del> τοῦ βασιλικοῦ γραμματέως πεφήναμεν 

    <lb n="32"/>ἀναίτιο<unclear reason="undefined">ι</unclear> <subst><add place="inline" cert="low"/><del rend="corrected">αναιτιο<unclear reason="undefined">ς</unclear></del></subst> ἐὰν φαίνηται προστάξαι ἀπο<unclear reason="undefined">σ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">τ</supplied>ε<supplied reason="lost">ῖ</supplied>λαι 

    <lb n="33"/>ἡμῶν τὴν ἔντευξιν ἐπ᾽ Ἀπολλώνιον τὸν <choice><corr>συγγενῆ</corr><sic>συγγενει</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="34"/>καὶ στρατηγὸν ὃς ἀκόλουθος ὢν τῆ<supplied reason="lost">ι ὑ</supplied>μετέρᾳ 

    <lb n="35"/>βουλήσει προνοεῖται ὡς οὐθεὶς <app type="BL"><lem resp="2.2.169; cf. 1.423"><seg cert="low">ἀναδική<supplied reason="lost">σει </supplied><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">ποτὲ</supplied></seg></lem><rdg>ἂ<unclear reason="undefined">ν</unclear> ἀδικη<gap reason="illegible" extent="4" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/></rdg></app> 

    <lb n="36"/>συκοφαντίας τε καὶ <choice><corr>διασεισμοῦ</corr><sic>διασισμου</sic></choice> χάριν ὅπως 

    <lb n="37"/>μηθενὶ ἐπιτρέπηι <app type="BL"><lem resp="1.423"><choice><corr>τὸ ἐπιὸν</corr><sic>τουπιον</sic></choice></lem><rdg>τ<gap reason="lost" extent="1" unit="character"/><unclear reason="undefined">υπ</unclear><gap reason="lost" extent="2" unit="character"/>ον</rdg></app> περὶ τῶν αὐτῶν 

    <lb n="38"/>παρενοχλεῖν ἡμᾶς μηδὲ περισπᾶν κατὰ 

    <lb n="39"/>μηδεμίαν παρεύρεσιν, ὅπως ὁ Μεγχῆς 

    <lb n="40"/>ἀνεμποδίστως τὰ <supplied reason="lost">τ</supplied>ῆς χρείας <choice><corr><supplied reason="omitted">σ</supplied>οι</corr><sic>οι</sic></choice> ἐκπλη-

    <lb n="41"/>ρώσηι, τετευχότες <supplied reason="lost">τ</supplied>ῆς παρ᾽ ὑμῶν 

    <lb n="42"/>εἰς ἅπαντα τὸν βίον ἀντιλήμψεως. 

    <lb n="43"/><choice><corr>εὐτυχεῖτε</corr><sic>ευτυχιτε</sic></choice>. 

    <lb n="44"/><handShift new="m2"/> Ἀπολλωνίωι.  ἐὰν ἦι οἷα <choice><corr>προφ<supplied reason="omitted">έρ</supplied>εται</corr><sic><subst><add place="inline">προφεται</add><del rend="corrected">προφονται</del></subst></sic></choice> προνοηθῆναι 

    <lb n="45"/>ὡς οὐ <subst><add place="inline"><add place="supralinear">παρενοχληθήσεται</add></add><del rend="corrected">περισπασθησονται</del></subst>  <expan><ex>ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="53">νγ</num> Παχὼν <subst><add place="inline"><num value="4">δ</num></add><del rend="corrected"><del rend="erasure">φ <gap reason="illegible" extent="unknown" unit="character" desc="vestiges"/></del></del></subst> </ab></div></div></body></text></TEI.2>